==概述==
2009年H1N1流感大流行是一場由[[流行性感冒|流感]]病毒新型[[株_(生物学)|变体]][[甲型H1N1流感|甲型H1N1流感]]所引发的全球性[[流行病|流行病]]疫情。最早的已知病例是2009年3月9日[[墨西哥|墨西哥]][[韋拉克魯斯市|韋拉克魯斯市]]格羅利亞的五歲小孩<ref>{{Cite news|last=Lacey|first=Marc|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2009/04/29/world/americas/29mexico.html|title=From Édgar, 5, Coughs Heard Round the World|date=2009-04-28|work=The New York Times|access-date=2020-02-21|language=en-US|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2020-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202014813/https://www.nytimes.com/2009/04/29/world/americas/29mexico.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="NYT6-23">{{Cite news | last = McNeil, Jr. | first = Donald G. | title = In New Theory, Swine Flu Started in Asia, Not Mexico | work = The New York Times | date = 2009-06-23 | url = https://www.nytimes.com/2009/06/24/health/24flu.html | accessdate = 2009-09-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090807164633/http://www.nytimes.com/2009/06/24/health/24flu.html | archivedate = 2009-08-07 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。3月17日開始有[[美國|美國]]病例，並於4月12日發生小範圍群聚感染<ref>{{cite web |author1=Central of Disease Control and Prevention |title=Outbreak of Swine-Origin Influenza A (H1N1) Virus Infection --- Mexico, March--April 2009 |url=https://www.cdc.gov/mmwR/preview/mmwrhtml/mm58d0430a2.htm |website=Central of Disease Control and Prevention |accessdate=2020-08-16 |archive-date=2009-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090606130423/http://www.cdc.gov/MMWR/preview/mmwrhtml/mm58d0430a2.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。4月15日於美國確診首例病患，疫情開始在[[美國|美國]][[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]]、[[德克薩斯州|德克薩斯州]]多处快速爆發，其後向墨西哥與美國以外的國家输出案例，疫情不斷蔓延<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/30386163/#storyContinued|title=Mexico flu deaths raise fears of global epidemic|publisher=MSNBC|date=2009-04-24|accessdate=2009-04-24|language=en|archive-date=2009-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090425133921/http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/30386163#storyContinued|dead-url=no}}</ref>。经估计，持续了一年多的疫情导致全球214个国家约7亿到14亿人感染<ref>{{Cite web|title=Study puts global 2009 H1N1 infection rate at 11% to 21%|url=http://www.cidrap.umn.edu/news-perspective/2011/08/study-puts-global-2009-h1n1-infection-rate-11-21|accessdate=2020-03-20|last=Aug 08|first=Robert Roos {{!}}|work=CIDRAP|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125151837/https://www.cidrap.umn.edu/news-perspective/2011/08/study-puts-global-2009-h1n1-infection-rate-11-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>，约150,000到575,000人死亡<ref>{{Cite web|title=First Global Estimates of 2009 H1N1 Pandemic Mortality Released by CDC-Led Collaboration {{!}} CDC|url=https://www.cdc.gov/flu/spotlights/pandemic-global-estimates.htm|accessdate=2020-03-20|date=2019-11-20|work=www.cdc.gov|language=en-us|archive-date=2020-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200303012120/https://www.cdc.gov/flu/spotlights/pandemic-global-estimates.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其中有明确统计的死亡病例约1.85万人<ref>{{cite news|title=世卫组织应对甲流疫情评估报告出台|url=http://news.sciencenet.cn/htmlnews/2011/3/245573.shtm|accessdate=2011-03-29|newspaper=科学网|date=2011-03-29|archive-date=2020-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130022143/http://news.sciencenet.cn/htmlnews/2011/3/245573.shtm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但世界卫生组织称实际死亡人数「毫无疑问更高」<ref>{{Cite web|title=WHO {{!}} Pandemic (H1N1) 2009 - update 100|url=https://www.who.int/csr/don/2010_05_14/en/|accessdate=2020-03-20|work=WHO|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127213417/https://www.who.int/csr/don/2010_05_14/en/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=H1N1 Still A Pandemic, Says WHO|url=https://www.redorbit.com/news/health/1893907/h1n1_still_a_pandemic_says_who/|accessdate=2020-03-20|date=2010-07-20|work=Redorbit|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201122141411/https://www.redorbit.com/news/health/1893907/h1n1_still_a_pandemic_says_who/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

中華人民共和國於5月10日發現首例確診，伴随着全球性大流行，到8月底为止的发展趋势相對还比较平静，但是在夏令营和学校开始出现了聚集性疫情，酝酿第二波爆发。9月起病例开始激增，10月28日当天发病人数超过3000人，达到了最高峰，高水平的发病态势持续到了年底。新年之后，逐渐消退。

2010年夏季内地甲流活动维持在较低水平，4月中旬以来，每周报告甲流感确诊病例数不超过30例，已连续12周无死亡病例。从2009年5月11日确诊首例甲型H1N1流感至2010年8月10日24时，中国内地累计报告甲流感确诊病例128033例，死亡805例。

